Param Info Dtype adhyaya Adhyaya from which shlokas are to be fetched int range Range of shlokas to be fetched [int, int] shlokas The shloka number of the shlokas to fetch [int, ...] Examples <p>python <pre><code>import requests

res = requests.post(
    "&lt;core endpoint&gt;/bhagavadgita/query", json={"adhyaya": 1, "range": [1, 5]}
)
res.raise_for_status()
data = res.json() # data var stores a list of shloka dictionaries.
</code></pre> typescript <pre><code>import axios from "axios";

const main = async ()=&gt;{
var res =  await axios.post("&lt;core endpoint&gt;/bhagavadgita/query",{
adhyaya: 1, shlokas: [1, 3, 4, 9]
})
const data = res.data // data stores Shloka objects in an array
}

main()
</code></pre></p>
